{"tid":2165937,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑避國安法 澳洲國際校校長辭職","createTime":"2020-08-20T06:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T06:34:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51dc9354205655bb1a69bd90ea39539936e2eb23","tid":2165937,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:30:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/SL6M3I55TVEJHJDVKWAGDGDMIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FSL6M3I55TVEJHJDVKWAGDGDMIQ%2F&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufbTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=314700eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200820%2FSL6M3I55TVEJHJDVKWAGDGDMIQ%2F&h=f341b7a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200820/SL6M3I55TVEJHJDVKWAGDGDMIQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n疑避國安法 澳洲國際校校長辭職<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/58fSxDkd_0eRUhcdC1Ldb1Kn2P0=/1057x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OIBNGCWQ3RHFVNW3MHHOGG6YHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F58fSxDkd_0eRUhcdC1Ldb1Kn2P0%3D%2F1057x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOIBNGCWQ3RHFVNW3MHHOGG6YHM.jpg&h=5363ef45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■澳洲國際學校校長Mark Hemphill疑憂國安法影響學校而辭任。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。有分析指疫情及國安法令本港國際學校流失人才。<br />\n<br />\n據悉尼晨鋒報（The Sydney Morning Herald）報道，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n教師料課程受京規管<br />\n<br />\n香港澳洲國際學校於2002年創立，全年學費約 13.7萬元，該校的課程包括教授六四事件。報道引述曾有份招攬Hemphill來港工作的澳洲教育家Bill McKeith形容，香港原有的現狀已被顛倒（the status quo has been thrown upside down），國家安全、隱私和法律等，正影響香港國際學校的治理及營運的方法。<br />\n<br />\n另一名國際學校教師亦在報道中指出，所屬學校的管理層擔心得罪北京及特區政府，預料學校的課程會受到攻擊，又指越來越多外籍教師感到困擾（all these new restrictions are starting to eat away at the expats living there）。<br />\n<br />\n報道另引述有本地學校教師擔心因參與示威活動或未能「正確」教授香港歷史，遭教局取消教師註冊；又指有特區政府官員建議在教室安裝攝影鏡頭，擔心有關數據會直接送中，「我看不到學術自由的未來（I can&rsquo;t see a future of academic freedom）」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/71y5wL2IyiSXRgaVjHi9r2ab6eQ=/1327x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MBTRSW5M5RADJNQH4QZM2NASUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F71y5wL2IyiSXRgaVjHi9r2ab6eQ%3D%2F1327x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMBTRSW5M5RADJNQH4QZM2NASUM.jpg&h=ce6358e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■澳洲國際學校"},{"pid":"9360b1acf5360927e50e7c601698ee69c1b170d7","tid":2165937,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"306fc99633b689dcf7a1cb9a036624c5f4beb74c","tid":2165937,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"不要做令澳洲成為澳洲人民共和國嘅幫兇<br />\n<br />\n十月狂歡 不日上映<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2165366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2165366</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"866273f9e3ba192c9c1b82b7a920ecc6d6c0b181","tid":2165937,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f667354e5ea2beddfa064b1d64b815b6950cf692","tid":2165937,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"人才唔走留係度做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}